data.description: Serene settings and endless adventure await at this beautiful home, located on the Blanche waterway, that leads directly to the Tchefuncte river. Residing at the end of a cul-de-sac, this home provides sanctuary from the hustle and bustle of the city while only a short drive away from it. It’s sizable 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms ensure everyone has a space to call their own. The open and airy living areas along with the wood burning stove offer a seamless connection to the great outdoors, ensuring you're always in touch with the natural beauty surrounding you. There is a large loft, located above the living areas, that can serve as an office, a playroom or anything else you can imagine! Make sure to step outside to your private backyard paradise, where an expansive deck, pool and outdoor bar invite you to soak up the sun, entertain with friends and family, or embark on thrilling water journeys. It’s time to enjoy living in a neighborhood with no HOA, Mandeville schools and all that life on the water has to offer!
